I will assume that you are using Unity, as you have not stated what `Time.deltaTime` is. You can use a flag for that:

    private bool increase = true;

    if (increase)
    {
        if (RotationCar &lt; 30)
            RotationCar += Time.deltaTime * 2;
        else
            increase = false;
    }
    else
    {
        if (RotationCar &gt; -30)
            RotationCar -= Time.deltaTime * 2;
        else
            increase = true;
    }

This way `RotationCar` is increased until its value is &gt;= 30, after that the flag is set to `false` so that the value is decreased in consecutive calls  to `Update` until its value is &lt;= -30. Then the flag is set to `true` and the process is repeated.

